  "1 < t < 3": "",
  "Set h > 53: -16t^2 + 64t + 5 > 53, so -16t^2 + 64t - 48 > 0, divide by -16: t^2 - 4t + 3 < 0, factor: (t-1)(t-3) < 0. Solution: 1 < t < 3.": "",
